                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6482" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0449</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8848 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京博家油站：从责权利走向共同富裕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jingbo Jia Oil Station: From Responsibilities, Rights and Benefits to Common Prosperity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵曙明，蔡静雯，王志成，陈嘉茜，胡雨欣，赵宜萱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵曙明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵曙明，蔡静雯，王志成，陈嘉茜，胡雨欣，赵宜萱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东京博新能源控股发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">责权利改革；共同体；共同富裕；2022百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Responsibilities, Rights and Benefits reform; Community; Common Prosperity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以山东京博控股集团新能源公司石经理重访第11加油站的场景为切入点，回顾了她从加油站员工做起，成长为公司中流砥柱的经历。京博控股集团通过“责权利”改革的层层推进，从激活员工活性出发，在“共生—共建—共富—共享”的演化过程中，帮助个体与组织逐步构建“达成共识、强化共生、促进共建、实现共富共享”的企业生态目标。由此，在集团内部形成休戚相关的命运共同体。本案例旨在引导学生透过石经理的视角，增强对利益共同体到事业共同体，再到命运共同体的理解，深刻感悟员工个体和组织之间的成就关系，理解在共同富裕的实现过程中，企业如何构建人人参与、人人尽力、人人共享的共建格局，真正实现个体的赋权和能力的提升，并以此为其他企业深化“责权利”改革，实现企业端共同富裕模式提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Starting from the scene where Ms. Shi, an employee of Shandong Jingbo Group New Energy Company, revisits the 11th gas station, this case reviews her experience from a gas station manager to a mainstay of the company. It is through the promotion of reform of “Responsibilities, rights and benefits” at all levels that the Chambroad Holding Group enables the assiduous activity of its employees. The evolution process of coexistence-co-construction- common prosperity-sharing&quot; facilitates individuals and organizations alike to gradually construct the corporate ecological goal of “reaching consensus, strengthening co-existence, promoting co-construction, and realizing co-prosperity and sharing”. As a result, a solidarity community of shared destiny is formed within the group. The purpose of this case is intended to guide students to enhance their understanding regarding the community of interests, the community of business, and the shared destiny through the perspective of Manager Shi, which aims to deeply understand the achievement relationship between individual employees and the organization, to know about how to build a co-construction pattern in which everyone participates, and everyone makes the greatest efforts and everyone shares in the realization of common prosperity so as to truly empower individuals and enhance their abilities, as well as to deepen the “responsibilities, rights and benefits” for other enterprises. Moreover, the initiative of reform directs focus at providing a reference for the realization of the common prosperity model pertaining to the side of enterprise.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用于企业管理课程中的“激励实务”或“人力资源视角下实现共同富裕”等知识技能的教学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益共同体：协同共生论、共同富裕-共生；事业共同体：利益相关者、共同富裕-共建；共同体理论：利益共同体、事业共同体、命运共同体、共同富裕-共富；综合激励模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
